title: Two girls fighting for an open spaghetti can.
subtitle: A video depicting a hard young woman's efforts to open a box of spaghetti-os, cheerful by the crowd, is actually excerpted from a piece of performance.
author: Kim LaCapria
vclaim: A video depicts a young woman struggling to open a box of spaghetti-os as a crowd watching and cheering for her ultimate hard-won victory.
